{"tid":2123470,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林明禎「及胸波浪長捲髮」新髮型曝光！　網驚：臉更小了","createTime":"2020-07-24T15:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T08:22:11.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e888284a4925706f8d319a8609712ac0d02e3562","tid":2123470,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:57:37.000Z","msg":"林明禎擁有天使臉孔和32E、22腰的魔鬼身材，被譽為「真人版娜美」，向來留著一頭俏麗短髮的她，24日突然在Instagram分享自己的長髮照，甜美模樣引來網友大讚。<br />\n<br />\n林明禎一直留著一頭招牌俏麗短髮，但她24日突然在Instagram發文寫下：「長短自如。」並PO出自己兩張留長髮的照片，只見她變成頂著一頭波浪長捲髮，模樣氣質又甜美。<br />\n<br />\n而林明禎長髮的新造型曝光後，引來網友紛紛留言大讚：「長短髮都正爆」、「完全不同的風格欸」、「長髮讓妳的臉顯得更小了」、「長髮實在太美」、「變一個人」。"},{"pid":"de451894dc0c59b41001dd185ce98db764a3ecc6","tid":2123470,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5027/d5027823.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5027%2Fd5027823.jpg&h=a481c723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5027/d5027824.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5027%2Fd5027824.jpg&h=ae44ce3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林明禎留長髮。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／林明禎）"},{"pid":"cdc101d5fa6eeb5c4059858813c98f85f455a23b","tid":2123470,"uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T15:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5027/d5027825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5027%2Fd5027825.jpg&h=62eecea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5027/d5027826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5027%2Fd5027826.jpg&h=ec61c947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林明禎一直留著短髮造型。（圖／翻攝自Instagram／林明禎）"},{"pid":"f45db95c7b57a35357fc2c159911b70b686f0c81","tid":2123470,"uid":63952,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"r